{"id": "1344846835767836692", "channel_id": "1344459007011717214", "type": 0, "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "author_bot": false, "content": "This team can help you cope with most occasions. red doll is an output character specialized for bosses, she doesn't have much output when facing normal monsters and elites, so you need to bring daffodil to help her transition. The other two characters are there to help her keep using her surefire moves, as red doll's damage relies heavily on her second form, which in turn relies heavily on her using her surefire moves over and over again.\nProbably the biggest downside to this team is that it's expensive to build.", "timestamp": "2025-02-28T01:41:11.693000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1344846835273175060", "filename": "c1dd0cdeae2ab4d9a4bf2ed81f909d43.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3852653, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1344459007011717214/1344846835273175060/c1dd0cdeae2ab4d9a4bf2ed81f909d43.png?ex=69cd2077&is=69cbcef7&hm=05c98d7e5871770cc55f0d5feadd27b1e5d319c258f4f7a10725042ac5655f82&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1344459007011717214", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Can anyone please tell me who are the characters that pair well with the red doll?", "forum_channel_id": "1304022827824844842"}
